http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/Driver-injured-as-truck-overturns-near-Aroor-bridge/article14013875.ece

One person was injured after a tipper truck overturned near Kumbalam-Aroor bridge on the National Highway here on Thursday.The police said the accident took place around 8 a.m. when the driver of the gravel-laden truck, proceeding to the Cherthala direction, lost control of the vehicle and hit another truck.Under its impact, the vehicle veered off to one side of the road and overturned after hitting the median.Gopi (48), driver of the tipper, sustained injuries and was hospitalized. Following the accident, traffic along the National Highway was disrupted for nearly an hour.